Class Summary
WolfSSL Base class which wraps the native WolfSSL embedded SSL library.
WolfSSLContext Wraps a native WolfSSL context object and contains methods directly related to the SSL/TLS context.
WolfSSLSession Wraps a native WolfSSL session object and contains methods directly related to the SSL/TLS session.
